summary: So my first half was interesting. My knee has been acting up and it definitely detracted from my race. I thought about it the...
body: So my first half was interesting. My knee has been acting up and it definitely detracted from my race. I thought about it the whole time, had to adjust so much to have the least discomfort possible. I went slower than I should’ve. The first half of the last 5k was brutal. But it was a beautiful day and I am so glad how it turned out. I do think my knee is a result of overtraining/doing too much too soon. Time to rest. My body is like broken so kinda have to anyways! On to the next:)
